INSTALLATION
================================================================================

For:
	Apple Binary and XML Property Lists

You must have:
	libxml2-dev
	cmake
	make
	gcc

Optional:
	swig
	python

To compile run:
	mkdir build
	cd build
	cmake ..
	make
	sudo make install  # (if you want to install it into your system directories)

On Ubuntu/Debian, you can do:
	sudo apt-get install build-essential cmake libxml2-dev


